Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:18.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&HDF01FD&\4c&HF8C191&}All that I need to know from you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1c&HDF01FD&\4c&HF8C191&}I know all of the baggage and burdens you carry beside you
